<i>I'm gettin' ready
for the big time</i>

121
00:05:47.038 --> 00:05:50.479
<i>Someday you're gonna
say I'm big time, too</i>

122
00:05:51.927 --> 00:05:53.873
Hey, little man!
Little Richard!

123
00:05:53.906 --> 00:05:54.936
Me and you, man!

124
00:05:54.968 --> 00:05:56.672
We're going to the top, baby!

125
00:05:56.673 --> 00:05:57.932
Big time!

126
00:05:58.120 --> 00:05:59.477
I ain't gonna
be ridin' this bike

127
