128
00:06:00.760 --> 00:06:01.842
You know what I'm sayin'?

129
00:06:01.874 --> 00:06:03.220
I'm gettin' a motorcycle, baby.

130
00:06:03.221 --> 00:06:04.741
We're gonna travel in style.

131
00:06:06.349 --> 00:06:09.452
<i>I'm gettin' ready
for the big time</i>

132
00:06:10.270 --> 00:06:12.257
<i>Someday I'm gonna
be in big time news</i>

133
00:06:12.855 --> 00:06:14.146
