You gotta take a dump?

137
00:06:23.283 --> 00:06:25.117
MAN: <i>We interrupt our regularly
scheduled program...</i>

138
00:06:25.118 --> 00:06:26.535
- What happened?
<i>...to bring you this special report.</i>

139
00:06:26.536 --> 00:06:27.537
(SHUSHING)

140
00:06:27.662 --> 00:06:29.963
<i>The shuttle Atlantis
exploded in space</i>

141
00:06:29.991 --> 00:06:32.291
<i>at 3:47 a.m., Eastern
Standard Time.</i>

142
00:06:32.292 --> 00:06:33.293
(GROWLING)

143
00:06:35.037 --> 00:06:36.059
