144
00:06:36.170 --> 00:06:37.216
Hey!

145
00:06:37.419 --> 00:06:38.505
Get, get.

146
00:06:38.506 --> 00:06:39.508
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

147
00:06:41.595 --> 00:06:43.094
That's my Godzilla.
Come on, now.

148
00:06:43.596 --> 00:06:44.597
Yo, fool!

149
00:06:44.630 --> 00:06:46.555
Don't be kickin' Little Richard.
What the hell your problem?

150
00:06:46.556 --> 00:06:48.278
