151
00:06:48.311 --> 00:06:49.891
What's a little runt like
you gonna do about it?

152
00:06:49.892 --> 00:06:52.060
Get him, Richard. Sic him.
If I wasn't no Christian,

153
00:06:52.061 --> 00:06:53.458
I'd be throwin' your fat

154
00:06:53.513 --> 00:06:54.997
