163
00:07:16.148 --> 00:07:18.420
Somebody shot, stabbed,
and it's Friday, payday.

164
00:07:18.421 --> 00:07:20.429
Dude, somebody probably didn't
get their paycheck.

165
00:07:20.462 --> 00:07:22.100
- Yes?
- I want to go shopping.

166
00:07:22.133 --> 00:07:23.631
