169
00:07:27.263 --> 00:07:28.805
- Little Richard!
- Right over there!

170
00:07:28.806 --> 00:07:30.043
(SCREAMING)

171
00:07:30.076 --> 00:07:31.350
I'm coming, Little Richard!

172
00:07:31.976 --> 00:07:33.764
Hang on, Little Richard. I'm comin'!

173
00:07:34.303 --> 00:07:35.371
(WHIMPERING)

174
00:07:35.605 --> 00:07:36.772
Don't you worry about it.

175
00:07:36.858 --> 00:07:38.178
I'm gonna get you outta there!

176
00:07:38.399 --> 00:07:39.439
You okay, buddy?

177
00:07:39.471 --> 00:07:41.209
Don't worry about it. Hang in there.

178
00:07:42.444 --> 00:07:44.498
Somebody dial 911!

179
00:07:44.614 --> 00:07:46.656
MAN: <i>My screen's full.
They're all over the place.</i>

180
00:07:46.657 --> 00:07:48.116
Bogies are breachin'
the atmosphere

181
