MAN 1: Get out of here!

206
00:08:59.444 --> 00:09:00.554
MAN 2: Oh, my god!

207
00:09:04.101 --> 00:09:05.202
(EXPLODING)

208
00:09:05.234 --> 00:09:06.522
(WOMAN SCREAMING)

209
00:09:09.374 --> 00:09:10.687
(SCREAMING CONTINUES)

210
00:09:11.617 --> 00:09:12.718
(GLASS SHATTERING)

211
