- That could take a week.

213
00:09:18.040 --> 00:09:18.872
Just find it, okay?

214
00:09:18.905 --> 00:09:20.625
I wanna know if the worst
is over or if it's on its way.

215
00:09:20.626 --> 00:09:22.419
We've got General Kimsey on the line.

216
00:09:22.420 --> 00:09:25.380
