what name's on the sign. I'm not...

333
00:13:41.137 --> 00:13:42.971
- What's goin' on here?
- What's goin' on?

334
00:13:42.972 --> 00:13:44.931
Well, I mean, you know,
I screwed up. I'm a little edgy.

335
00:13:44.932 --> 00:13:48.226
- How long you work for me?
- Five wonderful years.

336
00:13:48.227 --> 00:13:51.396
In five years, you have never
apologized to me this quickly.

337
00:13:51.397 --> 00:13:53.481
Something's going on here.
I'm gonna find out what it is.

338
00:13:53.482 --> 00:13:54.271
(STAMMERING)

339
00:13:54.299 --> 00:13:56.276
Well, I'm turning
over a new leaf.

340
00:13:56.277 --> 00:13:57.485
I'm trying to learn from the man.

341
00:13:57.486 --> 00:13:59.946
What would Harry do?

342
00:14:05.161 --> 00:14:07.423
