352
00:14:29.669 --> 00:14:30.815
Get up and get your clothes on.

353
00:14:34.607 --> 00:14:35.848
You just stay right there.

354
00:14:36.037 --> 00:14:37.059
I'll be right back.

355
00:14:44.186 --> 00:14:45.361
Here's what we're gonna do.

356
00:14:45.393 --> 00:14:46.993
I want every strategy we've got

357
00:14:46.994 --> 00:14:48.369
on near-Earth object collision.

358
00:14:48.370 --> 00:14:50.872
Okay? Any ideas, any programs,

359
00:14:50.873 --> 00:14:52.577
anything you sketched
on a pizza box...

360
00:14:52.609 --> 00:14:54.000
...or cocktail napkin.

361
00:14:54.001 --> 00:14:56.085
For 30 years,
they questioned the need for NASA.

362
00:14:56.086 --> 00:14:57.521
Today, we're gonna give 'em
the answer.

363
00:15:01.217 --> 00:15:02.623
You know about this, Rockhound?

364
00:15:03.429 --> 00:15:04.622
- You knew?
- No.

365
00:15:05.022 --> 00:15:06.256
I had no idea.

366
00:15:07.723 --> 00:15:08.730
Where's Harry?

367
00:15:09.975 --> 00:15:11.763
Harry, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

368
00:15:11.795 --> 00:15:13.272
I understand, okay?

369
00:15:13.305 --> 00:15:14.480
- You're mad.
- (GUN COCKS)

370
00:15:14.513 --> 00:15:15.615
Who wouldn't be mad?

371
00:15:15.648 --> 00:15:16.685
He's gonna shoot you.

372
00:15:16.718 --> 00:15:17.732
Nah, no, he's not.

373
00:15:17.733 --> 00:15:18.468
Oh, shit.

374
00:15:18.891 --> 00:15:19.898
Whoa!

375
00:15:20.655 --> 00:15:21.647
Aah!

376
00:15:21.946 --> 00:15:23.102
Harry!

377
00:15:23.586 --> 00:15:24.989
