just before he died...

388
00:15:42.700 --> 00:15:44.133
...that you would
take care of the boy.

389
00:15:44.134 --> 00:15:46.511
Now I'm not sure that
shootin' him is takin' care of him.

390
00:15:46.512 --> 00:15:47.679
