394
00:15:53.269 --> 00:15:54.936
you wanna kill
the best man on your crew,

395
00:15:54.937 --> 00:15:55.973
before we strike oil.

396
00:15:56.005 --> 00:15:57.438
Aw, Chick, I ain't
gonna kill him.

397
00:15:57.439 --> 00:15:58.537
Just gonna take a foot off.

398
00:15:58.570 --> 00:16:00.243
A man can work with one foot.

399
00:16:00.276 --> 00:16:02.052
You remember old
Frank Marx who worked...

400
00:16:02.084 --> 00:16:03.278
...with one hand
all them years?

401
00:16:03.279 --> 00:16:04.571
Yeah, but he wasn't very good.

402
00:16:04.572 --> 00:16:07.407
Harry, put the gun down!
You're acting insane!

403
00:16:07.408 --> 00:16:09.150
Now, honey, go get
some clothes on...

404
00:16:09.183 --> 00:16:10.034
...and get out of the way.

405
00:16:10.035 --> 00:16:11.739
You can't control my life!

406
00:16:12.056 --> 00:16:13.070
Fine.

407
00:16:13.103 --> 00:16:14.507
Clothes. Now!

408
00:16:14.540 --> 00:16:15.540
All right, stop! All right!

409
00:16:15.541 --> 00:16:17.548
It was funny for a minute.
It's not funny anymore.

410
00:16:19.420 --> 00:16:20.227
(EXCLAIMS)

411
00:16:20.775 --> 00:16:22.259
Harry, this is illegal, man.

412
00:16:22.548 --> 00:16:24.541
I'm temporarily insane,
Rock. It's all right.

413
00:16:25.112 --> 00:16:26.229
(A.J. SCREAMING)

414
00:16:29.805 --> 00:16:31.639
- Do I look like I'm crazy to you?
- Well...

415
00:16:31.640 --> 00:16:33.808
