00:17:05.507 --> 00:17:07.133
(STAMMERS)
we first got the idea

431
00:17:07.134 --> 00:17:09.093
the-the possibility
that-that a meteor or an asteroid...

432
00:17:09.094 --> 00:17:10.920
I need somebody who's
had a little less caffeine...

433
00:17:10.952 --> 00:17:11.930
