to the point of fracture.

437
00:17:18.979 --> 00:17:21.606
That's like shooting a B.B. gun
at a freight train, Doc.

438
00:17:21.607 --> 00:17:23.316
Uh, some of us have got this idea.

439
00:17:23.317 --> 00:17:24.853
We wanna land a craft...

440
00:17:24.885 --> 00:17:26.903
...deploy solar sails.

441
00:17:26.904 --> 00:17:28.732
You'll have a big canopy.

442
00:17:28.764 --> 00:17:30.817
Solar winds will
be caught by...

443
00:17:30.849 --> 00:17:32.208
...these Mylar sails.

444
00:17:33.786 --> 00:17:34.981
Come on, guys!

445
00:17:35.645 --> 00:17:37.538
We gotta come up with
something realistic here!

446
00:17:37.567 --> 00:17:38.802
We got 18 days!

447
00:17:39.291 --> 00:17:40.890
- (BEEPING RAPIDLY)
