Noonan's tattoos.

492
00:19:10.507 --> 00:19:13.301
Look, I was raised
on roughnecks by you.

493
00:19:13.302 --> 00:19:15.080
And now you get all
shocked and shaken...

494
00:19:15.108 --> 00:19:16.304
...when I fall in
love with one.

495
00:19:16.305 --> 00:19:18.222
So who's the hypocrite here,
Harry, huh?

496
00:19:18.223 --> 00:19:19.557
Look at those nice pipes.

497
00:19:19.558 --> 00:19:22.054
Listen to me, Grace.
- No, you listen to me, Harry.

498
00:19:22.082 --> 00:19:23.237
I grew up.

499
00:19:23.979 --> 00:19:26.555
TRUMAN: With the
proximity of the asteroid...

500
00:19:26.583 --> 00:19:27.648
...and no prep time,

501
00:19:27.649 --> 00:19:29.609
none of our primary plans can work.

502
00:19:29.610 --> 00:19:32.231
