504
00:19:33.822 --> 00:19:35.364
Terrible idea.

505
00:19:35.365 --> 00:19:37.492
Was I talkin' to you?

506
00:19:37.493 --> 00:19:39.494
This is Dr. Ronald Quincy
from Research.

