1509
01:03:06.432 --> 01:03:07.538
(CROWD CHEERING)

1510
01:03:17.610 --> 01:03:18.992
<i>I address you tonight,</i>

1511
01:03:20.321 --> 01:03:22.703
<i>not as the President
