1512
01:03:24.659 --> 01:03:26.281
<i>not as the leader of a country,</i>

1513
01:03:27.495 --> 01:03:29.735
<i>but as a citizen of humanity.</i>

1514
01:03:32.838 --> 01:03:35.914
<i>We are faced with the
very gravest of challenges.</i>

1515
01:03:37.964 --> 01:03:40.847
<i>The Bible calls this day
Armageddon.</i>

1516
01:03:41.288 --> 01:03:42.960
<i>The end of all things.</i>

1517
01:03:43.970 --> 01:03:47.382
<i>And yet, for the first time,</i>

1518
01:03:48.222 --> 01:03:49.717
<i>in the history of the planet,</i>

1519
