1524
01:04:05.408 --> 01:04:07.210
<i>is being called into service.</i>

1525
01:04:10.246 --> 01:04:13.790
<i>The human thirst for excellence,</i>

1526
01:04:13.791 --> 01:04:14.833
(TRANSLATOR ON RADIO)

1527
01:04:14.834 --> 01:04:15.841
<i>knowledge,</i>

1528
01:04:17.589 --> 01:04:20.591
<i>every step up the ladder of science,</i>

1529
01:04:21.841 --> 01:04:25.802
<i>every adventurous reach into space,</i>

1530
01:04:26.099 --> 01:04:29.701
<i>all of our combined
modern technologies and imaginations,</i>

1531
01:04:30.287 --> 01:04:33.748
<i>even the wars that we've fought,
have provided us the tools...</i>

1532
01:04:34.187 --> 01:04:36.099
<i>to wage this terrible battle.</i>

1533
01:04:37.774 --> 01:04:39.649
<i>Through all the chaos
that is our history,</i>

1534
01:04:39.650 --> 01:04:40.734
(TRANSLATOR ON TV)

1535
01:04:40.735 --> 01:04:43.695
<i>through all of the wrongs
and the discord,</i>

1536
01:04:43.696 --> 01:04:45.739
<i>through all of the pain and suffering,</i>

1537
01:04:45.740 --> 01:04:47.866
<i>through all of our times,</i>

1538
01:04:47.867 --> 01:04:50.202
<i>there is one thing
that has nourished our souls...</i>

1539
01:04:50.203 --> 01:04:52.871
<i>Mom, that salesman's on TV.</i>

1540
01:04:52.872 --> 01:04:56.082
<i>...and elevated our species
above its origins,</i>

1541
01:04:56.083 --> 01:04:58.444
<i>and that is our courage.</i>

1542
01:04:58.711 --> 01:05:01.880
<i>Dreams of an entire planet
are focused tonight</i>

1543
01:05:01.881 --> 01:05:05.029
<i>on those 14 brave souls</i>

1544
01:05:05.343 --> 01:05:07.677
<i>traveling into the heavens.</i>

1545
01:05:07.678 --> 01:05:09.888
<i>That man's not a salesman.</i>

1546
01:05:09.889 --> 01:05:11.223
<i>That's your daddy.</i>

1547
01:05:11.224 --> 01:05:12.390
<i>And may we all,</i>

1548
01:05:12.391 --> 01:05:14.115
<i>citizens the world over,</i>

1549
01:05:14.143 --> 01:05:16.016
<i>see these events through.</i>

1550
01:05:16.938 --> 01:05:18.234
<i>Godspeed...</i>

1551
01:05:19.016 --> 01:05:20.078
and good luck to you.

1552
01:05:27.782 --> 01:05:30.188
Freedom crew.
Independence crew.

1553
01:05:35.540 --> 01:05:36.563
How ya feelin'?

1554
01:05:36.916 --> 01:05:38.463
Uh, good, you know.

1555
01:05:38.492 --> 01:05:40.502
I mean, considering
I've never been

1556
01:05:40.503 --> 01:05:43.421
this scared in my entire life.
I... You know...

1557
01:05:43.422 --> 01:05:44.804
Listen. Once you get up there,

1558
01:05:45.360 --> 01:05:46.648
you're gonna be on your own.

1559
01:05:47.176 --> 01:05:48.484
If anything should happen,
I just wanted to...

1560
01:05:48.803 --> 01:05:50.468
I know, Harry.
I'll, uh,

1561
01:05:51.072 --> 01:05:52.507
try not to disappoint you.

1562
01:05:56.561 --> 01:05:57.812
Take care of yourself, kid.

1563
01:06:03.568 --> 01:06:04.802
MAN #1: <i>Freedom's on the bridge.</i>

1564
01:06:06.028 --> 01:06:09.091
<i>Attention in the firing room.
Oxidizer loading is complete.</i>

1565
01:06:11.075 --> 01:06:12.617
MAN #2: <i>Independence on the bridge.</i>

1566
01:06:12.618 --> 01:06:14.494
MAN #1: <i>Attention all personnel.</i>

1567
01:06:14.495 --> 01:06:17.135
<i>We are T-minus 2 hours
to the program goal.</i>

1568
01:06:26.424 --> 01:06:28.168
- Hey, Harry.
- HARRY: Yeah, Rock?

1569
01:06:28.509 --> 01:06:30.300
You know, we're
sittin' on four million

1570
01:06:30.328 --> 01:06:31.887
pounds of fuel,
one nuclear weapon

1571
01:06:31.888 --> 01:06:34.973
and a thing that has
270,000 moving parts

1572
01:06:34.974 --> 01:06:36.641
built by the lowest bidder.

1573
01:06:36.642 --> 01:06:37.684
(GRUNTS)

1574
01:06:37.685 --> 01:06:40.270
Makes you feel good, doesn't it?

1575
01:06:40.271 --> 01:06:41.599
Yeah.

1576
01:06:43.858 --> 01:06:46.318
- How ya doin', Oscar?
- Great.

1577
01:06:46.319 --> 01:06:48.904
I got that excited, scared feelin',

1578
01:06:48.905 --> 01:06:52.198
like 98 percent excited,
2 percent scared.

1579
01:06:52.199 --> 01:06:53.992
Maybe more. It could be 2...

1580
01:06:53.993 --> 01:06:56.036
It could be 98 percent scared,
2 percent excited.

1581
01:06:56.037 --> 01:06:59.789
But that's what makes it so intense,
is it's so confused.

1582
01:06:59.790 --> 01:07:01.833
I can't really figure it out.

1583
01:07:01.834 --> 01:07:04.502
Will you make mine really tight,
'cause I don't want to fall out?

1584
01:07:04.503 --> 01:07:07.088
I mean, almost to the point
of cutting off circulation.

1585
01:07:07.089 --> 01:07:08.143
(HARNESSES CLATTERS)

1586
01:07:08.466 --> 01:07:09.471
Ow.

1587
01:07:10.676 --> 01:07:13.094
It must be a comfort to know
that if the space program goes under,

1588
01:07:13.095 --> 01:07:15.358
you can always get a job
at Helga's House of Pain, huh?

