<i>- Trajectory.
- Go flight.</i>

1594
01:07:23.189 --> 01:07:24.606
<i>- FIDO.
- Go flight.</i>

1595
01:07:24.607 --> 01:07:25.774
<i>- EVA.
- Go flight.</i>

1596
01:07:25.775 --> 01:07:27.359
- <i>CAPCOM Freedom.</i>
- Go flight.

1597
01:07:27.360 --> 01:07:29.172
- CAPCOM Independence.
- Go flight.

1598
01:07:29.945 --> 01:07:31.977
All right, ladies and gentlemen,
it's pucker time.

1599
01:07:32.990 --> 01:07:35.533
MAN: <i>Independence and
Freedom, this is Kennedy firing room.</i>

1600
01:07:35.534 --> 01:07:37.285
<i>We're T-minus 1 minute.</i>

1601
01:07:37.286 --> 01:07:40.730
All crew members,
close and lock your visors.

1602
01:07:41.165 --> 01:07:42.942
<i>Independence, this
is launch control.</i>

1603
01:07:42.971 --> 01:07:45.085
<i>Be advised, we're
in a smooth count.</i>

1604
01:07:45.086 --> 01:07:46.397
T-minus 31.

1605
01:07:46.426 --> 01:07:48.380
You're go for auto-sequence start.

1606
01:07:48.381 --> 01:07:51.049
<i>P.L.T.s, perform your A.P.U. pre-start.</i>

1607
01:07:51.050 --> 01:07:52.286
