1619
01:08:17.243 --> 01:08:18.326
<i>We have main engine start.</i>

1620
01:08:18.327 --> 01:08:20.616
- <i>We have booster ignition.</i>
- We're going.

1621
01:08:21.914 --> 01:08:23.109
<i>And liftoff.</i>

1622
01:08:33.175 --> 01:08:34.337
<i>Freedom, this is flight deck.</i>

1623
